  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of 8 weeks of treatment
      with the combination regimen ABT-493/ABT-530 in comparison to sofosbuvir plus ribavirin for
      12 weeks in Hepatitis C Virus Genotype 2 (GT2) infected participants.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
